{"tid":2356778,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"人權組織轟大抓捕違國際公約","createTime":"2021-01-07T04:16:31.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-07T06:45:16.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"886256df7e30ecb00558f6cb1aeeca47f6493b03","tid":2356778,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T04:16:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210107/ZNSHUX6Z6NFNLFA3CN4WE4PCHA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210107%2FZNSHUX6Z6NFNLFA3CN4WE4PCHA%2F&d=tgCcTb3Ji4LFIEkqsM1g5gDpGYGFnKQRHckm7FIFNPY%3D&h=8b413879\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210107%2FZNSHUX6Z6NFNLFA3CN4WE4PCHA%2F&h=bfe628be\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210107/ZNSHUX6Z6NFNLFA3CN4WE4PCHA/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n人權組織轟大抓捕違國際公約<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/mFaw3z420CTV0GyozZ5pqYYdTYE=/1000x562/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/EKPJN2ZDF5A27FIU67UDVFXXLI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FmFaw3z420CTV0GyozZ5pqYYdTYE%3D%2F1000x562%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FEKPJN2ZDF5A27FIU67UDVFXXLI.jpg&h=7e7f599f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n國際特赦組織亞太區域主任Yamini Mishra<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】多個人權組織發聲批評特區政府將國安法變成打壓異見人士的武器，肆意踐踏及剝奪港人參與公共事務的權利及自由，違反《基本法》及《國際公民權利和政治權利公約》對人權的保障。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：國安歹毒：初選有罪  警拘戴耀廷53人<br />\n人民享從政合法權利<br />\n<br />\n國際特赦組織亞太區域主任Yamini Mishra回應稱，這場針對香港不同政治光譜反對派的打壓令人震驚，更凸顯了港版國安法已被用作對付敢於挑戰政權人士的武器。她形容拘捕行動印證了港版國安法適用範圍過於廣泛，令它可以在對國家安全沒有構成實際威脅的情況下也被濫用。<br />\n<br />\n她強調人民享有參與公共事務的合法權利。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：多國政要轟打壓「拜登站港人一方」 歐盟促放人 制裁擬升級<br />\n<br />\n「民權觀察」認為，事件再次反映政府運用國安法打壓異見，將和平參與公共事務的權利扭曲成罪行，嚴重踐踏《基本法》賦予港人的基本人權。《國際公民權利和政治權利公約》保障每個公民都有權利及機會直接或間接參與公共事務。立法會議員按照《基本法》和香港法律授予的職責及權力行事，包括提出彈劾行政長官、批准或否決公共財政預算，不論政府是否同意有關立場，均不應將其視為顛覆政權、危害國家安全的犯罪行為。<br />\n<br />\n民間人權陣線強烈譴責警方斷章取義詮釋法律，。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"0a9a3f100e08b7c11cb5cd7599b4f1d49447ac06","tid":2356778,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T06:44:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bb8162636fc752856ff97780ccee74ce3f72c29","tid":2356778,"uid":166462,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T06:44:55.000Z","msg":"石頭腳 完<br />\n繼續拉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86db5649d983e4723754f565ed27b11f4fdb09c7","tid":2356778,"uid":34010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T06:45:15.000Z","msg":"哦"},{"pid":"339e110033b3859c2db2b6b252ce9116b9090686","tid":2356778,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T06:45:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}